## How To Call From The CLI

<!--
What this section is for:
Show deterministic commands for users, scripts, CI, and agents that need JSON.

Include:
- Search.
- Info.
- Install.
- Evaluate.
- Remove when useful.
- Domain-specific scripts if the skill includes any.
-->

Search for the skill:

```text
python -m skillforge search "{{search_query}}" --json
```

Show skill metadata:

```text
python -m skillforge info {{skill_id}} --json
```

Install the skill into Codex:

```text
python -m skillforge install {{skill_id}} --scope global
```

Evaluate the skill before publishing changes:

```text
python -m skillforge evaluate {{skill_id}} --json
```

Remove the installed skill:

```text
python -m skillforge remove {{skill_id}} --scope global --yes
```

